title: Tajikistan Unemployment Rate
description: Unemployment Rate in Tajikistan increased to 7.50 percent in December from 2.10 percent in November of 2019. Unemployment Rate in Tajikistan averaged 2.42 percent from 2000 until 2019, reaching an all time high of 7.50 percent in December of 2019 and a record low of 2 percent in December of 2004. In Tajikistan, the unemployment rate measures the number of people actively looking for a job as a percentage of the labour force. This page provides - Tajikistan Unemployment Rate - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: National Bank of Tajikistan
